It is recommended to build them in this order:

Eina
Eet
Evas
Evas_Generic_Loaders
Ecore
Eio
Embryo
Edje
Efreet
E_Dbus
Eeze
Emotion
Ethumb
Elementary
Enlightenment (etc.)
Recommended requirements for all releases to the right are:

libc
libpthread
zlib
libfreetype/freetype
libfontconfig/fontconfig
libfribidi/fribidi (If you want BiDi support)
harfbuzz (If you want complex text shaping support)
opengl2.0/opengles-2 (depending on target)
libpng
libjpeg
libtiff
libgif
librsvg (if you want SVG support in Evas)
libx11
libxext
libxrender
libxcomposite
libxdamage
libxfixes
libxrandr
libxinerama
libxss
libxp
libxtest
libxdpms
libxcursor
libxprint
libxkbfile
libxcb
libxcb-keysyms
libxcb-shape
libssl/openssl
libcurl
libudev
libdbus
libasound/alsa (optional for mixer support)
libpoppler
libraw
libspectre
libgstreamer/gstreamer (and plugins - for emotion)
libxine (nice alternate codec for emotion
libvlc (nice alternate codec for emotion
lua5.1 or lua5.2 (not 5.0)
libwebp/webp (webp codec support for evas - optional)
